prose = """
Hi mom,

Just writing to tell you that I've quit my job as a OCCUPATION and I'm moving to COUNTRY. The truth is, I've always been passionate about PLURAL_NOUN, and COUNTRY is the best place in the world to build a career around them. I'll need to start small-- At first, all I'll be allowed to do is to VERB near them, but when people see how ADJECTIVE I can be, I'm sure to rise to the top.

Don't worry about me, and tell dad to take good care of my PERSONAL_ITEM. I'll be sure to call every HOLIDAY.

Love,

NAME
"""
newprose = prose

user_input = str(input("Please input an occupation:"))
newprose = newprose.replace("OCCUPATION", user_input) 

user_input = str(input("Please input a country:"))
newprose = newprose.replace("COUNTRY", user_input) 

user_input = str(input("Please input a plural noun:"))
newprose = newprose.replace("PLURAL_NOUN", user_input) 

user_input = str(input("Please input a verb:"))
newprose = newprose.replace("VERB", user_input) 

user_input = str(input("Please input an adjective:"))
newprose = newprose.replace("ADJECTIVE", user_input) 

user_input = str(input("Please input a personal item:"))
newprose = newprose.replace("PERSONAL_ITEM", user_input) 

user_input = str(input("Please input a holiday:"))
newprose = newprose.replace("HOLIDAY", user_input) 

user_input = str(input("Please input a name:"))
newprose = newprose.replace("NAME", user_input) 

print(newprose) 
